      <h2 class="t-heading t-scale-beta t-centered">Overview</h2>
      <p>The World Bank Group’s Public-Private Partnerships Cross-Cutting Solutions Area (PPP CCSA) is the clearinghouse for resources around public-private partnerships (PPPs), a collection produced by collaborative efforts of the Inter-American Development Bank (FOMIN), Asian Development Bank, African Development Bank, Islamic Development Bank, European Bank for Reconstruction and Development, PPIAF, and the PPPIRC.</p>
      <p>We partnered with the the PPP CCSA to showcase this knowledge by developing a collection of sites comprising the leading edge of PPP thought and knowledge, culminating in a central PPP Knowledge Lab.</p>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <% component "panel" do %>
